Pre-Game Insights: Both teams will be hoping to record their first win of the AFC Asian Cup 2023.
Lebanon fought bravely but eventually came up short against a strong Qatar side in a 3-0 defeat. On the other hand, China played a gritty goalless draw with Tajikistan and sit with just a point.
As both teams are direct competitors for the second qualifying spot that offers direct qualification into the Round of 16, winning the upcoming game becomes essential for them.
Predicted Line-up: Lebanon (3-5-2): Matar (GK), Michel, Nour, El Zein, Nassar, Shour, Haidar, Tneich, Zein, Jradi, Maatouk
China (5-3-2): Yan (GK), Liu, Zhang, Browning, Zhu, Yang Liu, Wang, Shangyung Wang, Tsun, Tan, Wu Lei
